** OAuth Python Library Example **

* Obtain a request token ...

FROM RESPONSE
key: 1724ada2e30c43e49219f770060c377c
secret: c26ae1b69785b89b98c2ef288d3d8edc
callback confirmed? true

* Authorize the request token in your browser

open: https://www.fitbit.com/oauth/authorize?oauth_token=1724ada2e30c43e49219f770060c377c

Verifier: 1c697ea7dd1558bdd9bfbebd18d16b7c
1c697ea7dd1558bdd9bfbebd18d16b7c

* Obtain an access token ...

REQUEST (via headers)

FROM RESPONSE
key: 7236ee8014b5d5f34789aa19cfe7aceb
secret: 264b69bf9d9d37f3856dd283ec7e707f

Done.